The "AcC jpr3-Ascalon sandy loam, 3 to 5 percent slopes" mapunit was combined with the "AcC 2tlnt-Ascalon sandy loam, 3 to 5 percent slopes" map unit as a result of the "SDJR - MLRA 67B - Ascalon sandy loam, 3-5% slopes" project". 

These projects were part of the Soil Data Join Recorrelation Initiative (SDJR). The tabular database was edited and populated according to guidance in National Instruction (NI-305) exhibits A and B.
